folder: Woodrow Road & Powell Street, Staten Island, NY
text:
(1)

1065 Woodrow Road, north side, between Powell Street and Lebanon Place (west of Huguenot Avenue), showing the Captain I. Cole House. It appears as having belonged to the Cole family on the maps from 1853 to 1917.

Spring 1924

P. L. Sperr

(2)

Another view of the Cole House, seen across Woodrow Road.

P. L. Sperr
Spring 1924
